						               													<description>Hexxed is a shedding or discarding game for 2-6 players. Players can shed more cards -- and force other players to take cards, by making combinations of six using the colors and numbers on the cards. Hexxed is fast moving and easy to learn. The deck features six colors in nine suits of eight cards each, or 72 cards in a Standard Deck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each Hexxed card has two colors and two numbers from 1-6. To play, match either of the colors on one of your cards with a color on the discard. Zero cards let you change the color for the next play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Special combos of six let you play again, or hex another player and make them take three cards. But, be careful. Your curse can come right back to you! The first player to empty their hand wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Spectrum Back design adds color and variety to the deck without revealing your cards. Try a Hexxed deck for your original games, magic tricks, and cardistry.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
